# AGENTS.local.md

Local-only instructions for this repository. Not committed.

## Purpose

Use this file for operator-specific guidance that is not repository policy.

## Good Candidates

- response style preferences
- private working conventions
- personal shortcuts and heuristics
- local machine or tool assumptions

## Do Not Put Here

- API keys, tokens, passwords
- shared project rules that collaborators need
- anything required for correct repository behavior

## Policy Boundary

Shared, public instructions belong in `AGENTS.md`.
Local overrides belong in `AGENTS.local.md`.
